<div class="main-content banner-content">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 hidden-lg hidden-md"><hr></div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <h2 class="banner-text">Be part of tomorrow's healthcare breakthroughs</h2>
        <p class="banner-text">When you participate in a University of Minnesota study, you can help create a healthier future.</p>
        <br>
        <div class="banner-text">
          <%= link_to 'Volunteer for a study', categories_path, class: 'btn btn-school btn-lg' %>
        </div>
        <br>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100 d-block d-sm-none"></div>
    <div class="col-md-8 visible-lg-block visible-md-block">
      <%= image_tag 'home-collage.jpg', class: 'pull-right visible-lg-block' %>
      <%= image_tag 'home-collage-condensed.jpg', class: 'pull-right visible-md-block' %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content home">
  <% unless @featured_category.blank? %>
    <div class="row home-content">
      <div class="col-md-2 featured-image">
        <%= link_to image_tag('covid.jpg'), studies_path(search: { category: @featured_category.try(:id) }), class: 'hyperlink-header', title: @featured_category.group_name %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 featured-content">
        <a href="<%=studies_path(search: { category: @featured_category.try(:id) })%>" title="<%=@featured_category.group_name %>"><h2 class="hyperlink-header">COVID-19 studies that need volunteers</h2></a>
        <p>The University of Minnesota has several clinical trials to test experimental medicines that could help those with coronavirus.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div class="row home-content well">
    <div class="col-md-6 search-form-content col-right-border">
      <h2>Find a study that's right for you</h2>
      <%= render 'shared/search_form' %>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100 d-block d-sm-none"></div>
    <div class="col-md-6 system-description">
      <h2><%= @system_info.system_header %></h2>
      <%= @system_info.system_description.html_safe %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row home-content">
    <div class="col-md-6 study-highlights">
      <h2>Studies at the University of Minnesota</h2>
      <p>The U of M conducts research on a wide range of health issues, from <a href='#{ !@cancer_category.nil? == true ? studies_path(search: { category: @cancer_category.try(:id) }) : studies_path }'>cancer</a> and <a href='#{ !@diabetes_category.nil? == true ? studies_path(search: { category: @diabetes_category.try(:id) }) : studies_path }'>diabetes</a> to <a href='#{ !@prevention_category.nil? == true ? studies_path(search: { category: @prevention_category.try(:id) }) : studies_path }'>prevention</a> and <a href='#{ !@womens_health_category.nil? == true ? studies_path(search: { category: @womens_health_category.try(:id) }) : studies_path }'>women's health</a>.</p>
      <p>Every study is different. Some studies need people with certain diseases or conditions, while others are open to healthy volunteers. One study may ask volunteers to go into a clinic, while others just ask that you complete a survey.</p>
      <p>There are many ways you can participate in U of M research, and thereâ€™s always a need for volunteers.</p>
      <%= link_to 'More about volunteering in research', "https://research.umn.edu/units/hrpp/research-participants/volunteering-research", class: 'btn btn-school btn-lg' %>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100 d-block d-sm-none"></div>
    <div class="col-md-6 system-description visible-lg-block visible-md-block">
      <%= image_tag 'campus-aerial.jpg', class: 'bordered' %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr/>
  
  <h2>More ways to get involved</h2>
  <div class="row">  
    <div class="col-md-6 rm-link col-right-border">
      <a href="https://researchmatch.org?rm=<%= @system_info.research_match_campaign %>" target:"_blank">
        <%= image_tag "researchmatch.png", class: 'pull-left' %>
        <h4 class="hyperlink-header">Research Match</h4>
      </a>
      <span>Complete a short questionnaire and you'll get matched to studies that are right for you.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100 d-block d-sm-none"></div>
    <div class="col-md-6 contact-link">
      <a href="<%=contact_index_path%>" title="Contact Us"><h4 class="hyperlink-header">Contact Us</h4></a>
      <span>Get answers to your questions or help finding a study.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
